      "text": "1989年のジャレコのビデオゲーム",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "wikidata"
    },
    {
      "text": "Pinball Quest is a 1989 pinball video game developed by Tose and published by Jaleco. Released for the Nintendo Entertainment System, Pinball Quest was unusual at the time of its release for its \"unique\" mash-up of pinball and role-playing game (RPG) mechanics, and it is considered the \"first ever RPG pinball game\".",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "『ピンボールクエスト』（PINBALL QUEST）は、トーセが開発しジャレコより1989年12月15日に発売されたファミリーコンピュータ用コンピュータピンボールゲーム。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "wikipedia_ja"
    }
